==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Troweled
<hw>Trow"eled</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>. <def>Formed with a trowel; smoothed
with a trowel; <as>as, <ex>troweled</ex> stucco, that is, stucco laid on
and ready for the reception of paint</as>.</def> <altsp>[Written also
<asp>trowelled</asp>.]</altsp>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Trowelful</ent>⟦br⟧
